URLNOTES: A cute hack to add annotations (like, say, a human translation) to any web page.

Run the sinatra app, then access /edit?url=<some URL you'd like to make notes about> in your favoritely flavored web-browser.

When you post the form the app will store your notes on the page in a DBM on the filesytem for posterity. The DBM is keyed on URLs. Simple, honest, and real.javascript:document.location="http://fi.ero.com:4567/edit?url="+document.URL